reviews.text:
These days, it can be hard to know what to believe online: brands keep a tight grip on any content posted online, carefully cleansing social networks of their customers’ least positive reviews and publishing the flattering testimonies of “imaginary customers” on their websites.
When we opted for total transparency, we wanted to apply this policy to all of our activities. For this reason, we have encouraged the freely-accessible publication of our customers’ experiences, so that every user can access impartial and honest information on our products.

Area is quite large, service is excellent.
Also food quality is the best

On our repeated request they put some beef pieces in the egg curry (We are not non-vegetarians).That shows a lack of interest in giving quality service.
They serve good lemon coffee.
Fortunately, language is not a problem as some of the staff members know and speak English.
Staffs are very nice and helpful.

reviews.text: 今日試左翠河菜色唔係太淡又太鹹，只得個睇相，奶茶，茶葉煮太過耐入口甘桔，自己衝都好飲過佢，服務態度超差入口門一開始就感覺自己欠佢錢甘，

店員態度極之差 服務不周到。。。
其實我連一分都唔想畀。。。

These days, it can be hard to know what to believe online: brands keep a tight grip on any content posted online, carefully cleansing social networks of their customers’ least positive reviews and publishing the flattering testimonies of “imaginary customers” on their websites.
When we opted for total transparency, we wanted to apply this policy to all of our activities. For this reason, we have encouraged the freely-accessible publication of our customers’ experiences, so that every user can access impartial and honest information on our products.
雖然唔係成日幫襯， 但係今日幫襯完都可以 blacklist，今日幫我哋落單嗰個阿姐啲服務態度衰到，真係要一路鬧人一路食
地方寛敞，座位較多。食物水準還可，價格合理
